      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BROOKLYN DAN (11) is a progressive colt who came from a similar barrier to this for a resuming win at Listed level at Melton. That took his strike rate at this distance range to 50 per cent and is a very strong form reference for this. The one to beat. YIRRADIVA (9) is back from a break of four-and-a-half months having gone to the paddock off a win at this circuit and distance. Fourth in a Group 1 fillies in Sydney two back. Draws for a trail and looks to be right up to the mark following a recent trial win. LOOKMEOVER NZ (4) looks close to a win after two successive placings. Draws lower and should be peaking now. CAPTURE OUR HEART NZ (6) draws lower so can progress off a nice return.",
